{"tid":1674612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【答謝藍絲員工】國泰向員工贈免費機票　聖誕新年都用得","createTime":"2019-10-25T09:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T04:47:55.000Z","uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":125,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b675259a601cb861c11ad15c62b206870ea5fd04","tid":1674612,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"國泰（293）今日再有新搞作。公司向國泰及國泰港龍合資格員工贈送免費機票，以答謝員工協助公司渡過艱難時期。不過，免費機票不適用於包括香港快運的國泰旗下附屬公司。<br />\n<br />\n公司今日向員工發出內部電郵，負責管理國泰航空所有人事策略及人力資源工作的人事董事Tom Owen在電郵中表示，過去一段日子全體員工均經歷非常困難的時期，期望是次旅遊福利可以答謝員工的專業和對公司作出的支持。"},{"pid":"5dae68519324b22a9525ae219ec72445f96090ca","tid":1674612,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54fa2766e790899129dc841f21bf9f63fe9c010a","tid":1674612,"uid":202464,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"間公司炒晒黃絲員工，淨底既全部都係愛國愛黨藍屍。"},{"pid":"ac71b0486f5da1c38614845155583b5732bd5791","tid":1674612,"uid":243407,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"班藍絲員工快啲客死異鄉"},{"pid":"86c50e800c3d3bec73aa6ca8da6f7740a3ee1fb9","tid":1674612,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"話時話，國泰公會肯罷工未？"},{"pid":"3666afa3c0d9405400041bbf4135f297ed98de67","tid":1674612,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54fa2766e790899129dc841f21bf9f63fe9c010a","tid":1674612,"uid":202464,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"間公司炒晒黃絲員工，淨底既全部都係愛國愛黨藍屍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:22:12.000Z","msg":"可以出全力抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdca09b4fe1d14f4153a1608712a7862bee1fd13","tid":1674612,"uid":108337,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"86c50e800c3d3bec73aa6ca8da6f7740a3ee1fb9","tid":1674612,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":3